    <updated>2017-06-30T18:08:57.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="文章頭格式上面那些"><a href="#文章頭格式上面那些" class="headerlink" title="文章頭格式上面那些  "></a>文章頭格式上面那些  </h2><p><code>fornt-matter</code> 的格式說明<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">使用的</span> <span class="string">Markdown語法備註</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="bullet">-06</span><span class="bullet">-27</span> <span class="number">20</span><span class="string">:46:38</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">Tech</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">[Hexo,Markdown,教學]</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">mathjax:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">layout:</span> <span class="string">page</span></div><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="文字斜體與粗體表示"><a href="#文字斜體與粗體表示" class="headerlink" title="文字斜體與粗體表示  "></a>文字斜體與粗體表示  </h1><p>使用 <code>_</code> 或是 <code>*</code> 表示<em>斜體</em>，使用 <code>__</code> 或是 <code>**</code> 表示<strong>粗體</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">*斜體* 或 <span class="keyword">_</span>斜體<span class="keyword">_</span></div><div class="line">**粗體** 或 <span class="keyword">_</span>粗體<span class="keyword">_</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="分隔線"><a href="#分隔線" class="headerlink" title="分隔線   "></a>分隔線   </h1><p>使用單行的 <code>___</code> 或是 <code>***</code> 表示。</p>
<h1 id="分級標題"><a href="#分級標題" class="headerlink" title="分級標題  "></a>分級標題  </h1><p>使用<code>===</code>表示一級標題，使用<code>---</code>表示二級標題。<br><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="section">這是一個一級標題</span></div><div class="line">===</div><div class="line"><span class="section">這是一個二級標題</span></div><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">### 這個可以表示三級標題</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>也可用<code>#</code>來定義：</p>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/# H1  </div><div class="line">/## H2</div><div class="line">/### H3</div><div class="line">/#### H4</div><div class="line">/##### H5</div><div class="line">/###### H6</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="刪除線"><a href="#刪除線" class="headerlink" title="刪除線  "></a>刪除線  </h1><p>使用的 <code>~~</code> 表示。<del>這句話刪除</del><br><figure class="highlight haml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">~~這句話刪除~~</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="超鏈結寫法"><a href="#超鏈結寫法" class="headerlink" title="超鏈結寫法  "></a>超鏈結寫法  </h1><h2 id="文字超鏈接"><a href="#文字超鏈接" class="headerlink" title="文字超鏈接"></a>文字超鏈接</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[<span class="string">Link name</span>](<span class="link">URL</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="圖片超鏈結寫法"><a href="#圖片超鏈結寫法" class="headerlink" title="圖片超鏈結寫法  "></a>圖片超鏈結寫法  </h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">！[<span class="string">PIC name</span>](<span class="link">PIC URL</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="youtube-內嵌法"><a href="#Youtube-內嵌法" class="headerlink" title="Youtube 內嵌法  "></a>Youtube 內嵌法  </h2><p>直接插入<code>iframe</code> 代碼<br><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/js/youtube-autoresizer.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"640"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"360"</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HfElOZSEqn4"</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用  "></a>引用  </h1><p>使用<code>&gt;</code> 表示<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">為何一直失敗</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<blockquote>
<p>為何一直失敗  </p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="表格寫法"><a href="#表格寫法" class="headerlink" title="表格寫法  "></a>表格寫法  </h1><p>绘制表格格式如下，·<code>|</code>控制分列，<code>-</code> 控制分行，<code>:</code> 控制对齐方式。<br><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Item     </span>|<span class="string"> Value     </span>|<span class="string"> Qty   </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> :------- </span>|<span class="string"> --------: </span>|<span class="string"> :---: </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Computer </span>|<span class="string"> 1600 USD  </span>|<span class="string"> 5     </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Phone    </span>|<span class="string"> 12 USD    </span>|<span class="string"> 12    </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Pipe     </span>|<span class="string"> 1 USD     </span>|<span class="string"> 234   </span>|</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h1 id="check-list-的寫法"><a href="#Check-List-的寫法" class="headerlink" title="Check List 的寫法"></a>Check List 的寫法</h1><ul>
<li>[ ] 支持以 PDF 格式导出文稿</li>
<li>[ ] 改进 Cmd 渲染算法，使用局部渲染技术提高渲染效率</li>
<li>[x] 新增 Todo 列表功能</li>
<li>[x] 修复 LaTex 公式渲染问题</li>
<li>[x] 新增 LaTex 公式编号功能</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="code-的寫法"><a href="#Code-的寫法" class="headerlink" title="Code 的寫法"></a>Code 的寫法</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">@requires_authorization</span></div><div class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">SomeClass</span>:</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">pass</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</div><div class="line">    <span class="comment"># A comment</span></div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">'hello world'</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="流程圖的寫法"><a href="#流程圖的寫法" class="headerlink" title="流程圖的寫法"></a>流程圖的寫法</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">st=&gt;start: Start</div><div class="line">op=&gt;operation: Your Operation</div><div class="line">cond=&gt;condition: Yes or No?</div><div class="line">e=&gt;end</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</div><div class="line">cond(yes)-&gt;e</div><div class="line">cond(no)-&gt;op</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="程序圖寫法"><a href="#程序圖寫法" class="headerlink" title="程序圖寫法"></a>程序圖寫法</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Alice-&gt;Bob: Hello Bob, how are you?</div><div class="line">Note right of Bob: Bob thinks</div><div class="line">Bob--&gt;Alice: I am good thanks!</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    
